{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/function-calc-no-invalid/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/font-family-no-duplicate-names/","description":"font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword 禁止在字体族名称列表中缺少通用字体族关键字。 这条规则会检查 font 和 font-family 属性。 选项 true 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword\"><a href=\"#font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword</h1>\n<p>禁止在字体族名称列表中缺少通用字体族关键字。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-family</span>: Arial, sans-serif; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**                     ↑\n *             一个通用族名称示例 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>这条规则会检查 <code>font</code> 和 <code>font-family</code> 属性。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-family</span>: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1em</span>/<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.3</span> Times; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-family</span>: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1em</span>/<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.3</span> Times, serif; }</code></pre>\n<p>使用与属性继承或系统字体值相关的关键字也<em>不</em>是违规行为。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: inherit; }\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: initial; }\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">i</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: unset; }\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">input</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font</span>: caption; }</code></pre>\n<p>通用族字体名称可以出现在字体列表的任意位置，这<em>不</em>会被认为是违规。换句话说，通用族字体名称不必是字体列表的最后一项。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">font-family</span>: Helvetica Neue, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/font-family-no-missing-generic-family-keyword/index.html.2a6175cf2f4957741e744ec2b62a3bef.json"}